[0.000, "o", "    Local:  http://localhost:13305\r\n    SSH:    ssh -L 13305:localhost:13305 52caee2a0699\r\n            then open http://localhost:13305\r\n\r\n  Gaia (manage agents):\r\n    Local:  http://localhost:4200\r\n    SSH:    ssh -L 4200:localhost:4200 52caee2a0699\r\n            then open http://localhost:4200\r\n\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  Claude Code (local AI coding agent):\r\n    lemonade launch claude -m <model-name>\r\n\r\n  в”Җв”Җ IMPORTANT в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ\r\n\r\n  Reboot your machine to start all services:\r\n\r\n    sudo reboot\r\n\r\n"]
